title: Inside the World's Highest Tech Prison.
description:
Exclusive access to the inside of one of the most technologically advanced prisons in the world, thanks to the Ministry of Justice - well that's not something I thought I'd ever do. After watching, I'm curious, does the way the prison works surprise you in any way?

I spend a LOT of time trying to make my videos as concise, polished and useful as possible for you - if you would like to support me on that mission then consider subscribing to the channel - you'd make my day 😁
